<!DOCTYPE html>
<html
	lang="en"
	data-theme="dark">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta
			name="viewport"
			content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

		<!-- Favicon -->
		<link
			rel="shortcut icon"
			href="/images/icons/favicon.ico"
			type="image/x-icon" />

		<!-- CSS -->
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/css/tailwindcss/tailwind.css" />

		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/css/remixicon/remixicon.css" />

		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/css/button-more.css" />

		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/css/overview.css" />

		<title>Overview Page</title>

		<!-- JS -->
		<script
			type="module"
			src="/js/navbar.js"
			defer></script>
		<script
			type="module"
			src="/js/toggleTheme.js"
			defer></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header><%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %></header>

		<main>
			<section class="w-full min-h-screen">
				<!-- Banner -->
				<div class="relative h-[300px] md:h-[400px] overflow-hidden mt-16 md:mt-18">
					<img
						src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1208/94745l.webp"
						alt="Anime Banner"
						class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover blur-sm scale-110" />

					<!-- Banner Overlay -->
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-transparent to-(--bg-primary)"></div>
				</div>

				<!-- Content Container -->
				<div
					class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between -mt-36 md:-mt-32 px-4 relative z-10">
					<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10">
						<!-- Poster Button -->
						<div class="shrink-0">
							<img
								src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1208/94745l.webp"
								alt="Title Here"
								class="image-poster w-48 md:w-56 rounded-lg shadow-2xl border-2 mb-4" />

							<button class="btn-add-to-list w-48 md:w-56 py-2 rounded-md">
								<i class="ri-add-line"></i>
								<span>Add to list</span>
							</button>
						</div>

						<!-- Title Info -->
						<div class="title-info flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
							<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood</h1>

							<!-- Title Rating, Type, Status -->
							<div class="flex gap-2">
								<div class="title-rating flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
									<i class="ri-star-fill text-sm"></i>
									<p class="text-sm">10</p>
								</div>

								<div class="title-type flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
									<p class="text-sm">TV</p>
								</div>

								<div class="title-status flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
									<p class="text-sm">Finished</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<!-- Title Synopsis -->
							<div
								class="relative max-h-60 md:max-h-68 overflow-y-auto pr-4 lg:pr-16 scrollbar-thin scrollbar-thumb-[#4c566a] scrollbar-track-[#3b4252]">
								<p class="title-synopsis mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
									After a horrific alchemy experiment goes wrong in the Elric household, brothers
									Edward and Alphonse are left in a catastrophic new reality. Ignoring the
									alchemical principle banning human transmutation, the boys attempted to bring
									their recently deceased mother back to life. Instead, they suffered brutal
									personal loss: Alphonse's body disintegrated while Edward lost a leg and then
									sacrificed an arm to keep Alphonse's soul in the physical realm by binding it to a
									hulking suit of armor.\n\nThe brothers are rescued by their neighbor Pinako
									Rockbell and her granddaughter Winry. Known as a bio-mechanical engineering
									prodigy, Winry creates prosthetic limbs for Edward by utilizing \"automail,\" a
									tough, versatile metal used in robots and combat armor. After years of training,
									the Elric brothers set off on a quest to restore their bodies by locating the
									Philosopher's Stoneâ€”a powerful gem that allows an alchemist to defy the
									traditional laws of Equivalent Exchange.\n\nAs Edward becomes an infamous
									alchemist and gains the nickname \"Fullmetal,\" the boys' journey embroils them in
									a growing conspiracy that threatens the fate of the world.\n\n[Written by MAL
									Rewrite]
								</p>
							</div>

							<!-- Title Meta -->
							<!-- TODO: Make grid layout for meta title -->
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
